      <h1 class="display-1">Mortgages for Aviation Professionals</h1>
      <p class="lead hero-subtitle">Aviation pay is the most misunderstood income structure in U.S. consumer lending. Per diem, overtime, locality, premium pay, future Captain rate, IA certification, facility upgrade. Most lenders refuse to count any of it. We read your contract and qualify you on what you actually earn &mdash; whether you fly the line, work the cabin, turn wrenches, or work the scope.</p>

      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/schedule-call" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Talk to Our Team</a>
        <a href="#professions" class="btn btn-secondary btn-large">Find your profession</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-trust">
        <span class="trust-dot"></span>
        <span>Broker NMLS #1072866</span>
        <span>&middot;</span>
        <span>Specialist in aviation-industry &amp; variable-income mortgages</span>
      </div>
        </div>
        <figure class="hero-image">
          <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/5778355/pexels-photo-5778355.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1200" alt="Airline pilot and flight attendant in uniform standing together at an airport" width="1200" height="1500" loading="lazy" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/1200x1500/0A0E1A/E8EEFF/png?text=Aviation+Professionals';">
