        <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: var(--s-5); font-size: var(--text-sm); line-height: 1.7; list-style: none;">
          <li>→ <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/aviation-professionals/pilot/">Pilot aviation mortgage guide</a></li>
          <li>→ <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/aviation-professionals/flight-attendant/">Flight attendant aviation mortgage guide</a></li>
          <li>→ <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/aviation-professionals/aircraft-mechanic/">Aircraft mechanic aviation mortgage guide</a></li>
          <li>→ <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/aviation-professionals/air-traffic-controller/">Air traffic controller aviation mortgage guide</a></li>
          <li>→ <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/purchase-inquiry/">Start your aviation mortgage pre-approval</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SOURCES -->
  <section class="sources-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header" style="text-align: center; max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto var(--s-8);">
        <div class="eyebrow">References</div>
        <h2>Sources &amp; further reading.</h2>
        <p>Aviation mortgage qualification involves federal regulations, profession-specific union contracts, and Fannie Mae/Freddie Mac variable-income guidelines. These are the authoritative sources spanning all four aviation professions we serve. All links open in a new tab.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="sources-grid">

        <div class="source-group">
          <h4>Federal &amp; Regulatory</h4>
          <ul class="source-list">
            <li>
              <a href="https://www.faa.gov" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                <span class="source-name">Federal Aviation Administration (FAA)</span>
                <span class="source-url">faa.gov</span>
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://www.bls.gov/ooh/transportation-and-material-moving/home.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
